name: Login, list post, edit and delete post

elements.name: Ingresar con cuenta válida, Listar Posts, Editar Post (500 caracteres), Listar Posts

steps.name: I enter "<USER>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-posts-list-item"
I click on element having css selector "textarea"
I enter "<BIG_TITLE>" into input field having css selector "textarea"
I enter "<DESCRIPTION_POST_EDIT>" into input field having css selector "p"
